casebody.data:
Treziyah TOMA, Plaintiff-Appellant,
and
St. Peter Medical Center and LN Transportation, Intervening Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
AUTO CLUB INSURANCE ASSOCIATION, Defendant. SC: 155860
COA: 330585 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 3, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's February 20, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
